&lt;p&gt;「接着，当培根炸成8成熟的时候，我们就可以运功发力，翻转一下锅，用力把培根盖在猪头上，一道香喷喷的培根盖猪头就好了。」&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://qstatic.zuimeia.com/img/article/6310/821fa9308ac85bf547061af3ef55233f_832x1556.JPG?imageMogr/v2/gravity/South/crop/!832x1556-0-0&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;107&quot; height=&quot;200&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;「当然，不喜欢猪头的同学也可以用抽水马桶代替。」&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://qstatic.zuimeia.com/img/article/6310/1cdf110703e7aab5a1f31f143a0b64d2_1125x2436.PNG?imageMogr/v2/gravity/South/crop/!1125x2436-0-0&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;92&quot; height=&quot;200&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
